people have never set foot in — pre-war boilers under Church Street office buildings, steam radiators in 1910s East Nashville bungalows, restaurant kitchens up and down Broadway, and now tankless installs in Brentwood new-builds. Frank Sullivan is the licensed master plumber on record. The phone gets answered live, the truck shows up when we say it will, and the quote you get is flat-price and itemized."," ",["$","em",null,{"children":"Honest and reliable plumbing — that's been the entire business model since 1895."}]]}]]}]]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-bone-100/60 border-b border-ink/10 py-10","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8","children":[["$","div","Years in Nashville",{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-forest leading-none","children":"131"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-xs text-ink-muted uppercase tracking-wider mt-2","children":"Years in Nashville"}]]}],["$","div","Generation Sullivans",{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-forest leading-none","children":"5th"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-xs text-ink-muted uppercase tracking-wider mt-2","children":"Generation Sullivans"}]]}],["$","div","Licensed & insured",{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-forest leading-none","children":"100%"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-xs text-ink-muted uppercase tracking-wider mt-2","children":"Licensed & insured"}]]}],["$","div","Price quotes always",{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-forest leading-none","children":"Flat"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-xs text-ink-muted uppercase tracking-wider mt-2","children":"Price quotes always"}]]}]]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"py-16 lg:py-24","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"eyebrow mb-3","children":"Our story"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-ink mb-9 leading-tight","children":"How a one-shop Nashville plumber became a five-generation family business."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose-editorial","children":[["$","p",null,{"children":["Joe B. Sullivan founded the company in ",1895,", when Nashville was still a city of about 80,000 people, water mains were just being run to outlying neighborhoods, and indoor plumbing was a new luxury most homes were still adding. Joe B. learned the trade as an apprentice, got his master plumber ticket, and started running calls out of a shop near downtown with a horse-drawn wagon to haul fixtures."]}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The business passed from Joe B. to his sons, then to his grandsons, then to his great-grandsons — each generation training the next, each generation keeping the same name on the door. We've moved the shop a few times (we're now at 292 Hermitage Avenue in East Nashville), upgraded the trucks from wagons to vans, swapped lead and galvanized fittings for PEX and copper, and added authorized warranty service for AO Smith, Bradford White, State Industries, and Whirlpool — but the rest of the operation has stayed remarkably consistent for 130+ years."}],["$","p",null,{"children":["Today Frank Sullivan is the licensed master plumber on record, and ","Joe B. Sullivan & Sons"," serves Davidson and Williamson counties — East Nashville and the urban core, Belle Meade and Forest Hills, Green Hills and Hillsboro Village, Brentwood and Franklin in Williamson. We do both commercial and residential, with a particular specialty in commercial water heater and boiler service. The phone still gets answered live, the trucks still show up on time, and the name on the door is still Sullivan."]}]]}]]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-forest text-bone-50 py-16 lg:py-24","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"eyebrow text-copper-light mb-3","children":"How we work"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display text-3xl lg:text-4xl mb-12 leading-tight max-w-2xl","children":["Four promises we make on"," ",["$","span",null,{"className":"italic","children":"every single job."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8","children":[["$","div","Flat-price quotes, no surprises",{"className":"border-l-2 border-copper pl-6 py-2","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-display text-xs tracking-[0.2em] text-copper-light","children":"01"}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl mt-2 mb-3","children":"Flat-price quotes, no surprises"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-bone-100/80 leading-relaxed","children":"Every job is quoted as a flat price after diagnosis — parts, labor, permit, haul-away, and warranty registration all itemized. No per-hour open meter, no mid-job upcharges, no 'we found something extra' once we've started. The number we tell you up front is the number you pay."}]]}],["$","div","Licensed master plumber on every job",{"className":"border-l-2 border-copper pl-6 py-2","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-display text-xs tracking-[0.2em] text-copper-light","children":"02"}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl mt-2 mb-3","children":"Licensed master plumber on every job"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-bone-100/80 leading-relaxed","children":"Frank Sullivan is the licensed Tennessee master plumber on record for every Joe B. Sullivan & Sons job. Verifiable on the state board. Every install and repair is supervised by a licensed master plumber — not handed off to an apprentice running solo."}]]}],["$","div","Honest answers about repair vs. replace",{"className":"border-l-2 border-copper pl-6 py-2","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-display text-xs tracking-[0.2em] text-copper-light","children":"03"}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl mt-2 mb-3","